{"tid":2369054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來真係會有人從此佔領你內心的一小角","createTime":"2021-01-16T18:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T05:06:26.000Z","uid":246901,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b1a9f11ae6644e983a4dba4c61023ffe3f7546","tid":2369054,"uid":246901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:04:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">失戀後<br />\n差唔多成半年都以淚洗面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有半年我都懷疑自己係色盲，<br />\n因為成個世界都係灰色。<br />\n我都深知道，<br />\n佢從來都無對我動過真情<br />\n<br />\n過咗幾年後的今天，<br />\n我已經同佢無任何聯絡，<br />\n大家的人生都展開新一頁。<br />\n唔係刻意去記起，<br />\n但係時不時就會諗番起當年。<br />\n我覺得我係對佢已經無感情<br />\n<br />\n只係覺得心口有啲痛，<br />\n就算幾努力，都係難以忘記<br />\n原來心一旦有缺口，就唔會好似一開始咁完整。<br />\n即使你唔願意，<br />\n有啲人就係咁一世佔領你內心的一小角。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b75eec4b658b1d5eacff1215074a2b46c3144995","tid":2369054,"uid":246901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">大家有無同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e037b4cedf880893f3e33defe658e36760736e6f","tid":2369054,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97bc38761748624a69474308035478d865ff594","tid":2369054,"uid":246901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e037b4cedf880893f3e33defe658e36760736e6f","tid":2369054,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">Ching有故事分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"86c37d6cf42d376ae7285642fb18d8dcc3734faa","tid":2369054,"uid":388755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"sc